::Aerotaur/*******::
       He smiles at the good news and knocks on the observation window to get 
Windlord's attention.  "I need to go get my shot, Windlord.  I'll talk to you 
again soon."  With that he turns and runs off to find Wheeljack-X and his 
vaccine.

       Elsewhere on the planet the bot that had slipped between dimensions 
awakes unaware of where he is or how he got there.  He shrugs off his 
confusion and transforms into a sleek drake and flies off circling a 
prominent mountain peak and trying to regain his bearings.

--part1_1c6.6ebbb83.2baa904a_boundary
